babel: Faʻamatalaga a le tagata faʻaaoga Babelu
babel-1: Lenei tagata mafai sao ma se laugatasi le [[$1|mea muamua]] o [[$2|$3]].
babel-2: O lenei tagata faʻaaoga e iai le poto masani [[$1|nisi]] i le [[$2|$3]].
babel-0-n: Lenei tagata faʻaaoga e leai se malamalama i le gagana Samoa (pe malamalama i ai ma le faigata tele).
babel-1-n: Lenei tagata mafai sao ma se laugatasi le [[$1|mea muamua]] o [[$2|gagana samoa]].
babel-2-n: Lenei tagata mafai sao ma se laugatasi le [[$1|feololo]] o [[$2|gagana Samoa]].
babel-3-n: Lenei tagata faʻaaoga ua i ai le malamalama [[$1|loloto]] i le [[$2|gagana Samoa]].
